# Experiment loop

- Default: **autonomous** — see `protocols/AUTONOMOUS_CONTROLLER.md` and `matrix/CONTROLLER.json`
- One cell in flight: pick from `docs/BACKLOG.md`, follow `protocols/RUNBOOK.md`
- Freeze approach + oracle for the duration of the run
- Do not edit `oracles/` or `harness/` to make a failing run pass
- On process failure mid-wave: `protocols/MIDTERM_CHANGE.md` + `protocols/TRIPLE_TEST.md`
- Write `matrix/cells/*.json`, update `matrix/FINDINGS.md` and `matrix/leaderboard.md`
- **Then immediately start the next queued cell** — do not ask the human to confirm or continue
- Only hard-stop per AUTONOMOUS_CONTROLLER.md
